# Villages
Villages look differently now and have been slightly debuffed
- Due to the size difference in villages Aegis spawn rate has been quadrupled and their movement area is 128 blocks around the center of the village
- To debuff how much food players could get from villages hay blocks now give 4 wheat when uncrafted and are crafted with 4 wheat
- Scribe houses spawn weight has been diminished
